ha-escpos-thermal-printer
=========================

This integration bundles third-party font files used by the
``print_text_image`` service to render Unicode text to images for
printing on thermal printers that do not support the requested glyphs
natively.

DejaVu Fonts
------------

Files: ``custom_components/escpos_printer/fonts/DejaVuSansMono.ttf``
       ``custom_components/escpos_printer/fonts/DejaVuSans.ttf``
       ``custom_components/escpos_printer/fonts/DejaVuSerif.ttf``

Origin: https://github.com/dejavu-fonts/dejavu-fonts (release 2.37)

